{"tid":1892042,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚瞓覺發夢俾隻狗用電槍之類嘅嘢係咁電，電死寶寶了","createTime":"2020-02-22T09:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T11:55:52.000Z","uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef549572135d4f991ca8e743c368e0ee1714e153","tid":1892042,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"冇記錯個夢係唔知做喺街，然後有隻痴線狗乸衝過嚟要搜我身，然後我一拎轉身就攞嘢電鳩我，我越嗌救命佢就電得越勁，佢隔離另一個女警，好似靚女嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉住佢都唔肯停，起勢咁電鳩me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後突然有個手足唔知係飛出嚟一腳踢開個狗乸，然後我本能意識一招廬山昇龍霸打落隻狗乸度，點知一招就打死咗隻狗乸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我就乖乖地俾個靚女女警拉，完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個夢大概係咁，啲細節位唔係好記得，淨係知個夢好逼真，俾人電嗰陣真係好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270e034f30a255483d3eb220f473c5481c275425","tid":1892042,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:33:02.000Z","msg":"真係夢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1ec9e44a0170bb5c5e1ac295699cd4ab29bfce","tid":1892042,"uid":196326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c8d3d53e76a07889100d31b5fbd2be82c81f12","tid":1892042,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa1ec9e44a0170bb5c5e1ac295699cd4ab29bfce","tid":1892042,"uid":196326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"我都覺得好膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=